metadata.name: SPKTRL Mint Pass
metadata.description:
UNIT: SPKTRL QC-725

DATA: The SPKTRL Quantum Containment Vessel—the QC-725 (the first of its kind)—was developed in response to the need of securely transporting inter-dimensional beings to the SPKTRL research and processing facilities located in every corner of the multiverse.

INSTRUCTIONS: Engaging the electromagnetic ion trap causes the inter-dimensional being to become trapped in phase with the device in the physical plane. The QC-725 renders all inter-dimensional travel impossible by blocking the quantum entanglement with particles in other dimensions and districts.

WARNING: The Quantum Shielding Mechanism is to be used only for temporary transport purposes and should never, under any circumstance, be used for long-term confinement. A core meltdown must be avoided at all cost.
